snippet.title: Spinnin' Flare - Android Game | Intro
snippet.description:
Tap and hit the glows, complete as many levels as you can!

◇ Spinnin' Flare is finally here! ◇

Get into the game!

★ Infinite number of levels! ★
★ Procedurally generated glows! ★
★ Amazing visual effects! ★
★ Multiple combo variations! ★
★ Many awesome achievements! ★
★ World leaderboards! ★
★ and many more! ★

Get it on Google Play: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Zenith.Merge
